.IR $ZPWR/env/.zpwr_env.sh
and
.IR $ZPWR/env/.zpwr_re_env.sh .
Override any of them in
.I $ZPWR/local/.tokens.sh
(git-ignored).
.I $ZPWR/env/.zpwr_re_env.sh
is re-read after the user tokens file so dependent variables update.
